# 🔐 Password Generator

A clean, minimal password generator built with **HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript**. Instantly generate strong, customizable passwords right in the browser — no frameworks, no dependencies.

---

## 📽️ Demo

<!-- Add your demo GIF below -->
![Demo](./assets/demo.gif)

---

## ✨ Features

- Set password length using a slider (1–20 characters)
- Choose character types: Uppercase, Lowercase, Numbers, Symbols
- Password strength indicator (Weak / Medium / Strong)
- One-click copy to clipboard with visual feedback
- Shuffled output — no predictable patterns
- Fully responsive UI

---

