```

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

No install needed. Just open the project locally:

1. Clone or download this repo
2. Open `index.html` in your browser

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/password-generator.git
cd password-generator
# Open index.html in browser
```

---

## 🧠 How It Works

1. User selects desired character types via checkboxes
2. Password length is set via slider
3. On clicking **Generate Password**:
   - At least one character from each selected type is guaranteed
   - Remaining characters are filled randomly from selected types
   - The full password is **shuffled** using Fisher-Yates algorithm to avoid predictable order
4. Strength is calculated based on character variety and length

### Strength Rules

| Condition | Strength |
|-----------|----------|
| All types checked + length ≥ 12 | 🟢 Strong |
| Mixed types + length ≥ 8 | 🟡 Medium |
| Anything else | 🔴 Weak |

